1712
02:31:11,180 --> 02:31:14,090
'There will be more tales?'

1713
02:31:14,090 --> 02:31:20,210
'Here, sir, there are always more tales.'

1714
02:31:20,210 --> 02:31:27,090
That evening was some time ago, and my memory
