1716
02:31:32,399 --> 02:31:39,350
perfect clarity the stab of fear that went
through me when Stevens swung the oaken door

1717
02:31:39,350 --> 02:31:46,800
wide-the cold certainty that I would see that
alien landscape, cracked and hellish in the

1718
02:31:46,800 --> 02:31:53,670
bloody light of those double suns, which might
set and bring on an unspeakable darkness of

1719
02:31:53,670 --> 02:32:00,131
an hour's duration, or ten hours, or ten thousand
years. I cannot explain it, but I tell you

1720
